_sText:
Bhop_barry_pepega is the first map in a series of three maps, each made by a different owner of Barry's Bhop Servers.

The map is around 3-5 minutes long, and not very difficult.
There is a list of music credits at the end of the map.
There is also a bonus level in the map.

This is the first map I've made in 7 years, I hope you all enjoy it :)
